The '''1900 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their tenth ever season of organized football. The Keydets went 4-1-2 under their new head coach [[Sam Walker (American football)|Sam Walker]].<ref name="VMI">http://www.vmikeydets.com/pdf8/708636.pdf</ref>
